Data.Name: Trapezoidal profile 35/207 Profiled sheets made of steel for roof, wall and deck constructions
Publisher: European Association for Panels and Profiles
Data.Description: Prefabricated thin walled profiled sheets made of steel for load-bearing, self-supporting and non-supporting application in single- and double-layer roof, wall and ceiling structures. The profiled sheets are made of a core of steel, which is protected against corrosion with zinc and organic coatings.
